  "body": "I keep hitting this issue on my L2 geth node and dtl, using the docker compose from this repo and using latest image versions\r\n```\r\nREPOSITORY                              TAG       IMAGE ID       CREATED        SIZE\r\nethereumoptimism/data-transport-layer   latest    1630753f0b5b   2 hours ago    1.9GB\r\nethereumoptimism/l2geth                 latest    6ff486e590cb   2 hours ago    41.6MB\r\n```\r\n\r\nDTL configs\r\n```\r\nDATA_TRANSPORT_LAYER__POLLING_INTERVAL=200\r\nDATA_TRANSPORT_LAYER__CONFIRMATIONS=0\r\nROLLUP_POLL_INTERVAL_FLAG=50ms\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\nERROR[06-15|20:33:43.031] Problem committing transaction           msg=\"nonce too high\"\r\nERROR[06-15|20:33:43.031] Got error waiting for transaction to be added to chain msg=\"nonce too high\"\r\nERROR[06-15|20:33:43.031] Could not verify                         error=\"Verifier cannot sync transactions with BackendL2: Verifier cannot sync transactions with backend l2: Cannot sync transactions with backend l2: Cannot apply transaction: nonce too high\"\r\nINFO [06-15|20:33:43.080] Syncing transaction range                start=11669197 end=11844273 backend=l2\r\nDEBUG[06-15|20:33:43.081] Applying transaction to tip              index=11669197 hash=0x43f4b9d673d83a9cadaf721b0c140103ff1c9a4c58e7d3f03da057938c35874f origin=sequencer\r\nDEBUG[06-15|20:33:43.081] Attempting to commit rollup transaction  hash=0x43f4b9d673d83a9cadaf721b0c140103ff1c9a4c58e7d3f03da057938c35874f\r\n ```\r\n\r\nWhenever I hit this, I have to re-sync with my snapshots from https://archive.org/download/optimism-snapshot\r\n\r\nOn nodes where I set POLLING_INTERVAL to 5s, it doesn't seem to hit this issue.\r\nI think sometimes the RPC gives back a bad result or when throttled, it might feed corrupt data into the L2GETH",
